lead_paragraph: Wolverhampton Wanderers have sacked manager Kenny Jackett just over a week after China-based Fosun Group took over the English Championship club from long-standing owner Steve Morgan.

headline.print_headline: No Jackett Required as Wolves Sack Manager
headline.main: No Jackett Required as Wolves Sack Manager
